Microsoft Windows 7 Build 7057 Ultimate ( 64bit )

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is newest leaked version of Windows 7.

3,19 GB (3 430 977 536 bytes)

7057.0.090305-2000_x64fre_client_en-us_Retail_Ultimate-GB1CULXFRER_EN_DVD

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

There are lots of changes in this new build. Some of them are as follows:

    * The infamous UAC issue has been fixed. In previous Windows 7 builds when you changed the UAC level, Windows didn't show any prompt message. It was dangerous from security point of view as a malware can turn off UAC on a system easily.
    * New user display pics
    * New Wallpapers
    * New Icons for few programs
    * New login screen
